Citation.sTitle: Heat Capacities of 2-Propenol and Selected Cyclohexylalcohols
Citation.sAbstract: Isobaric heat capacities of four selected alcohols (cyclohexanemethanol, CAS RN 100-49-2; cyclohexaneethanol, CAS RN 4442- 79-9; cyclohexanepropanol, CAS RN 1124-63-6; 2-propenol, CAS RN 107-18-6) were measured with highly sensitive Tian-Calvet calorimeter in the temperature range from 254 K to 352 K. Phase behavior was investigated with a differential scanning calorimeter. Experimental heat capacity data were correlated as a function of temperature. The main aim of this work was to fill the gap in the reliable heat capacity data for these compounds.
